KinectMultiTouch 

See it in action here: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YwEeFQw8QlI 

Tools used: 

- openFrameworks with Code::Blocks
- Armadallio, linear algebra library
- OpenNI, Kinect driver

Reference: 
- keyboard-anywhere: 
    - https://github.com/petermoz/keyboard-anywhere
- Kinect Windows 7 Mouse Control V2 Demo 
    - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlwWp8ItCVA
